'''冰河湖'''（Jökulsárlón）是[[冰岛|冰岛]]最著名和最大的[[冰川湖|冰川湖]]。它位于冰岛东南部，[[瓦特纳冰原|瓦特纳冰原]]的南端。冰河湖于1934-35年开始出现，由于冰岛冰川的大量融化，从1970年代开始，冰河湖的面积不断扩大，如今面积为18平方公里。湖深200米，为冰岛第二深湖。<ref name=Jokul>{{Cite web|url=http://www.simnet.is/gardarj/tmap/lon.htm|title=Jökulsárlón|accessdate=2010-10-13|publisher=Virtually Virtual Iceland|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110517123438/http://www.simnet.is/gardarj/tmap/lon.htm|archivedate=2011-05-17}}</ref><ref name=Stone>{{Cite book|last=Stone|first=Andrew|title=Scandinavian Europe|page=268|accessdate=2010-10-13|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=fULqNyVRakkC&pg=PA268|publisher=Lonely Planet|year=2009|isbn=1741049288|archive-date=2014-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140627191117/http://books.google.com/books?id=fULqNyVRakkC&pg=PA268|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Iceland>{{Cite web|url=http://iceland.vefur.is/iceland_travel_info/Sightseeing/jokulsarlon.htm|title=Jokulsarlon Glacier Lagoon|accessdate=2010-10-13|publisher=Iceland on the web|archive-date=2010-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100506014519/http://iceland.vefur.is/Iceland_travel_info/Sightseeing/jokulsarlon.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Evans>{{Cite book|last=Evans|first=Andrew|title=Iceland|page=389|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=9_GfdBAASUQC&pg=PA389|publisher=Bradt Travel Guides|year=2008|isbn=184162215X|access-date=2011-01-01|archive-date=2014-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140627191028/http://books.google.com/books?id=9_GfdBAASUQC&pg=PA389|dead-url=no}}</ref>杰古沙龙冰河湖对面的黑沙滩上搁浅着许多被海浪冲回岸边的冰石，被称作“钻石冰沙滩”<ref>Nanna Gunnarsdóttir: [http://cn.guidetoiceland.is/best-of-iceland/jokulsarlon-glacier-lagoon-the-crown-jewel-of-iceland-s-nature 杰古沙龙冰河湖－冰岛自然王冠上最耀眼的宝石] {{Wayback|url=http://cn.guidetoiceland.is/best-of-iceland/jokulsarlon-glacier-lagoon-the-crown-jewel-of-iceland-s-nature |date=20160625015646 }}</ref>。

